Program: Outlook
Title: Mandela - The Private Life of A Public Man
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/w3cswlls
Last Broadcast Date: Thu 19 Jul 2018
It's 100 years since an icon was born. Nelson Mandela is being celebrated around the world for the historic shifts he brought about in his home country of South Africa, but what about the private man? In this special episode of Outlook we go beyond the public figure and learn about the interior world of a very public figure. Show less